-agribusiness-pact/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Phenomenal World</a> ) <em>see also</em> <strong>Global Race for Lithium Lands in Rural Brazil</strong> : International mining companies arrive in Jequitinhonha Valley, promising development and provoking concerns about local compensation and water scarcity. ( <a href="https://nacla.org/global-race-lithium-brazil" target="_blank" rel="noopener">NACLA</a> )</p><p> • <strong>Yes, there is a cure for bullshit</strong> The patron saint of calling BS, Harry Frankfurt, died watching his philosophy become more urgent than ever. (<a href="https://nautil.us/yes-there-is-a-cure-for-bullshit-354730/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Nautilus</a> )</p><p> • <strong>The Owls Are Not What They Seem</strong> : The birds possess even uncannier powers than we&#39;ve imagined. ( <a href="https://www.theatlantic.com/magazine/archive/2023/09/owl-senses-smart-animal-intelligence/674769/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">The Atlantic</a> )</p><p> • <strong>How to Avoid Looking Like a Fool, Iowa State Fair Edition</strong> : Presidential candidates find the annual fair can be an obstacle course. Don&#39;t flip the pork chops too fast, watch out for the corn dogs. （ <a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/iowa-state-fair-campaign-corn-dog-presidential-candidate-ec9a6680" target="_blank" rel="noopener">华尔街日报</a>）</p><p> • <strong>The Most Emotional Video Game Music in the Unlikeliest of Places</strong> The Eleanor Rigby of video game music. ( <a href="https://nordic.ign.com/donkey-kong-country/70353/feature/the-most-emotional-video-game-music-in-the-unlikeliest-of-places" target="_blank" rel="noopener">IGN</a> )</p></blockquote><p>请务必查看我们最新的<a href="https://ritholtz.com/category/podcast/mib/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" data-web-url="http://www.bloombergview.com/topics/masters-in-business">商业硕士</a><a href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/podcast/masters-in-business/id730188152?mt=2" data-web-url="https://itunes.apple.com/us/podcast/mas